Used for: Vocabulary selection (which words to include in the deck)

The HSK 3.0 repository incorporates data from:
- SUBTLEX-CH (CC BY-SA 4.0) - frequency ordering
- Pleco HSK 3.0 word lists (MIT) - word selection methodology

